name: Galaxy Rush (Misteeps)
description:
Run through vibrant levels in space.

Shoot activators to clear obstacles and open paths.

Slow down time and weave through the many deadly lasers in your path.

-

Music not included in itch.io release.

Performance may be laggy on specific browser + hardware combinations.

-

Made for Replit's Kajam 2021 (Oct. 18 - Oct. 25).

Original Release : https://replit.com/@Misteeps/Galaxy-Rush

Source Code : https://github.com/Misteeps/Galaxy-Rush
